{"tid":1572483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有關今晚皇后像廣場中環站外，懷疑有人被手足襲擊至骨折事故","createTime":"2019-09-15T16:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T10:51:37.000Z","uid":23094,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4e425b22fd7b46a0f03def366ca0036b08e50ebe","tid":1572483,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"當時7點半左右，大家開始散緊<br />\n去到皇后像廣場中環站<br />\n突然間有人話有人打手足<br />\n跟住成班人追住其中一個疑犯<br />\n嗰個疑犯MK Look黑衫黑口罩<br />\n一開波好似畀其他手足打咗幾嘢<br />\n跟住佢聲稱係自己人，大家停咗手<br />\n然後要求佢同傷者對質<br />\n<br />\n由於當時現場有風吹話有狗<br />\n所以有Gear走咗先<br />\n聽講冇Gear嘅就留低咗同疑犯重組案情<br />\n<br />\n我想問最後件事嘅真相係點？<br />\n嗰幾位被襲擊嘅手足而家情況如何？<br />\n有冇在場手足講下當時情況？"},{"pid":"dc1654ecad8151a14e63e3b99ec334c1ce8b5c96","tid":1572483,"uid":103870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:38:32.000Z","msg":"有時打人之前要睇清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc43f4d9d0c6d56e614c52c19447431d7ccb9237","tid":1572483,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"求真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d5f46810547f987a367cb337d95defbc3a3fcd","tid":1572483,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:45:21.000Z","msg":"求真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70e0f4ef5d88ad30427745c7a20307a97c12cd1","tid":1572483,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"即係點？有臥底扮捉鬼打手足？"},{"pid":"d58766a16f86c6e673c55bbc3785ab6a7f1b5ac6","tid":1572483,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d70e0f4ef5d88ad30427745c7a20307a97c12cd1","tid":1572483,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"即係點？有臥底扮捉鬼打手足？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:53:43.000Z","msg":"以我所知當時有兩個男仔<br />\n都被懷疑有份襲擊手足<br />\n都係黑衫黑口罩，其中一個有戴耳環<br />